a photorealistic close-up portrait of a forest spirit, emerging from a misty, dark forest. Her physique is formed from interwoven leaves and vines, with pale green skin that blends into the bark of the trees around her. Her hair is made of cascading leaves, adorned with golden, glowing seed pods that provide a soft illumination in the gloomy setting. The trees are twisted and barren, with crows flying above, adding a sense of movement and unease to the scene. Her gaze is intense yet calm, as if she is the guardian of the forest’s secrets, embodying both its beauty and its dangers.

The background is filled with mist, obscuring the path behind her and creating a mysterious ambiance. The light is muted, casting shadows that emphasize the textures of her leafy body and the reflective wetness of the forest floor. The contrast between her green, life-filled form and the dark, decaying forest evokes a balance between growth and death, light and darkness. Aim for a hyper-realistic style that brings out the intricate details of her leaf-textured skin, the glowing seed pods, and the eerie, desolate beauty of the forest.

Looking directly at the camera with an intense stare, her form both blending with and standing out from the dark, decaying forest.
